        <h1 class="heading">Solutions</h1>
        <h3> The decision-making process involved close collaboration among my team members, each contributing valuable insights into
        the design and functionality of the website. Visual prototypes were crucial in visualizing the selected color palette
        and layout. The team focused on simplicity to enhance user experience and ensure that visitors could easily find the
        information they were looking for.
</h3>
        <div class="container solutions-container">
            
            <div class="solutions">
                <img src="./min.png" alt="">
                <h2>Color Palette Selection</h2>
                <p>After thorough research and consideration, my team opted for a vibrant orange color that exuded energy
                    and excitement,
                    aligning perfectly with the park's ambiance.
                </p>
               
            </div>
    
           
            <div class="solutions">
